Dan Trachtenberg is an American filmmaker and podcast host .
He directed the 2016 film 10 Cloverfield Lane .
Trachtenberg was one of three hosts of The Totally Rad Show and a former co-host of Geekdrome .
Both programs were hosted at Revision3 .
Trachtenberg is also the director of the 2011 short film Portal : No Escape , an episode of Black Mirror entitled `` Playtest '' and the director of various television commercials and public service announcements .